text: I remember I was in my large tent, there was an old oak tree trunk stump with thick roots sticking out from the earth, that is where he came out from the hollow hole and offered me a large book.” “What book?” Mike probed.
Mother Earth News has recycling ideas: Cut the Christmas tree trunk & use the stump as a decorative piece or display in your yard.
